								<p style="color: black;">Your Rating: &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

								<p id="star_grade" style="font-size: 20px;">
									<a href="#none" id="star1" class="on">★</a> <a href="#none"
										id="star2" class="on">★</a> <a href="#none" id="star3"
